    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ARDS (Berlin Definition Criteria) or mechanical ventilation in healthy lungs

        Exclusion Criteria:

